data.description: This is a MUST See, completely updated home!! Taken down to the studs this home has been completely remodeled. This Charming cottage provides an open floor plan with a welcoming patio- covered entrance.  This 3 bedroom 2 bath home sits on a nice quite street, with plenty of space in the backyard for all your summer family gatherings! Home features laminate floors, decorative lights throughout, home also has fresh paint , all updated plumbing , updated electric , roof installed 2021, and Additional square footage added to provide a master bath and dining room! This is one you do not want to miss!! Welcome home to modern country living!!
